title: 6: In Five Years
itunes:title: In Five Years
description: It's the First Thursday in May and the newest episode of The Readheads Book Club is here! The girls are recapping and discussing In Five Years by Rebecca Searle. They're sharing all of their favorite parts, the things that most surprised them, and who they saw as each character. Plus they're sharing all of the other books that they read this month and whether or not they think you should read them too! The next book is Jackie's choice and she chose The Glass Hotel by Emily St. John Mandel. Follow @thereadheads on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thereadheads/ Join our Facebook group: https://www.facebook.com/groups/thereadheads/ Submit a question or comment to us at thereadheadsbookclub@gmail.com Update Description The overall Readheads Rating for In Five Years is 3.5 stars.
